QuestData.Title: Not in Chee-Chee's Backyard
QuestData.Description: Not all hozen are the same. Chee-Chee's tribe was forest hozen... came from Jade Forest. Pretty easy to get along with.$b$bThe Kunzen invaders... they come from mountains, far to the north. Not nearly as nice as Chee-Chee.$b$bThey come into our green land, take our things, leave big mess behind.$b$bChee-Chee wants to kill them. You like to help?
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 8 members of the Kunzen tribe in the Kunzen Village.
